<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Us</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f5f7;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            color: #222;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .message {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border-left: 4px solid #007BFF;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #007BFF;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Dear <%= name %>,</h1>
        <p>Thank you for contacting us! We have received your message and will get back to you shortly.</p>

        <p><strong>Your message:</strong></p>

        <div class="message">
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any urgent questions, please feel free to <a href="mailto:moruditech@gmail.com">reach out to us directly</a>.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>Your Eagles View Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
